Subject: [RFC PATCH 2/4] uapi: asm-generic: mman-common: add
 MADV_KV_HOT/EVICT/PREFETCH
Message-ID: <20260506-kv-cpu-madvise-rfc-v1-2@gmail.com>
In-Reply-To: <20260506-kv-cpu-madvise-rfc-v1-0@gmail.com>
